custom-block.l: We move the right magnet to the right of the left magnet to look at adjacent pairs
We compare the ball above the left magnet with the ball above the right magnet

custom-block.l: This algorithm, like when ordering cards in your hand, takes each ball and inserts it in the correct position among the balls already ordered to its left by shifting to the right all the balls to its left that are bigger than it. When the rightmost ball is inserted at its place the algorithm ends. _______________ Put stepping to 0 to avoid stepping. Otherwise press SPACE to do one step.

custom-block.s: move %s magnet under ball in first position

custom-block.l: We leave the first ball where it is as there are no balls to its left where it can be inserted

custom-block.s: move %s magnet one position to the %s

custom-block.l: We move the left magnet to the right to look for the next ball to be inserted in the correct position
This is the ball we want to insert in its correct position between the balls to its left

custom-block.s: move right magnet to the %s of left magnet

custom-block.l: We start looking at the immediate left of the left magnet to find the position where it can be inserted
We compare the ball above the left magnet with the ball above the right magnet

custom-block.s: shift ball on %s magnet one position to the %s

custom-block.l: The ball on right magnet is bigger than the ball on left magnet, so we put it back one position to the righe

custom-block.s: move %s magnet one position to the %s

custom-block.l: We keep looking for the correct place where to insert the ball on the left magnet

custom-block.s: move %s magnet one position to the %s

custom-block.l: We keep looking for the correct place where to insert the ball on the left magnet
We compare the ball above the left magnet with the ball above the right magnet
The ball to the left is smaller than the ball to the right, so we found where to insert the ball on the left magnet

custom-block.s: move %s magnet one position to the %s

custom-block.l: The ball on the left magnet must be inserted here
We swap the magnets to keep track of where to restart the insertion procedure
We insert the ball on the left magnet in its correct position
We swap the magnets again to find the next ball to be inserted

custom-block.s: move %s magnet one position to the %s

custom-block.l: We move the left magnet to the right to look for the next ball to be inserted in the correct position
There are no more balls to order. The sorting is finished.
